project_id.description: A unique identifier for the project, hashed from the project name

user_id.description: A unique identifier for the user

send_anonymous_usage_stats.description: Whether dbt is configured to send anonymous usage statistics

adapter_type.description: The type name of the adapter

nodes.description: The nodes defined in the dbt project and its dependencies

sources.description: The sources defined in the dbt project and its dependencies

macros.description: The macros defined in the dbt project and its dependencies

docs.description: The docs defined in the dbt project and its dependencies

exposures.description: The exposures defined in the dbt project and its dependencies

metrics.description: The metrics defined in the dbt project and its dependencies

groups.description: The groups defined in the dbt project

disabled.description: A mapping of the disabled nodes in the target

parent_map.description: A mapping from child nodes to their dependencies

child_map.description: A mapping from parent nodes to their dependents

group_map.description: A mapping from group names to their nodes

saved_queries.description: The saved queries defined in the dbt project

semantic_models.description: The semantic models defined in the dbt project
